reviewText: Super, love this! Such a nice gift!
My sons really enjoy all the activity and music going on.  I love being able to switch up DVDs for more entertainment.

My son truly enjoyed his Baby Einstein collection, I think this is what made him love classical music, I put it since he was about a month old until he was about 3.  They are also very educative, a great introduction to various languages since they come with the option of being played also in Spanish and French.
